Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微軟雅黑\bord0\cH&000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(640,674)}——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是能讓我依靠的人 無論是誰都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是能保護你的人 應該也無論是誰都無所謂喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若葉同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！若葉同學不是那種人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由乃就不行啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微軟雅黑\bord0\cH&000000&\fscy200\fscx120\an5\pos(600,689)}——
