Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你是…由乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一段時間不見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種意義上…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:39.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你在說什麼啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 順利的讓時間倒流了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
