Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus的核心啊 把2nd變小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬰…嬰兒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:23:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你是…由乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一段時間不見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種意義上…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你在說什麼啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:12.09,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:15.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總覺得很感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.93,0:23:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.01,0:23:16.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭討厭討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus的核心啊 把2nd變小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 你的…胸…
